name: create
description: Triggered when a branch or tag is created.

name: delete
description: Triggered when a branch or tag is deleted.

name: discussion
description: Triggered when a discussion event is received from GitHub.

name: error
description: Emitted when an error occurs inside the GitHub webhook logic.

name: fork
description: Triggered when a fork event is received from GitHub.

name: issues
description: Triggered when an issue event is received from GitHub.

name: issue_comment
description: Triggered when a comment is created on an issue or pull request.

name: label
description: Triggered when a label is created, edited, or deleted.

name: milestone
description: Triggered when a milestone is created, closed, opened, edited, or deleted.

name: project
description: Triggered when a project is created, updated, or deleted.

name: project_card
description: Triggered when a project card is created, moved, edited, or deleted.

name: pull_request
description: Triggered when a pull request event is received from GitHub.

name: pull_request_review
description: Triggered when a review is submitted on a pull request.

name: push
description: Triggered when a push event is received from GitHub.

name: release
description: Triggered when a release event is received from GitHub.

name: repository
description: Triggered when a repository is created, renamed, archived, or transferred.

name: star
description: Triggered when a star event is received from GitHub.
